snippet.title: Longplay - Dune (DOS)
snippet.description:
I play Dune for DOS. I've beaten it many times, but this is not my best time. I once beat it in exactly sixty days.

Never tried the vegetation route, though.

Captured through DOSBox.

Bandcamp for the composer of the soundtrack, Stéphane Picq:
https://stphanepicq.bandcamp.com/

Stéphane Picq's YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/@StephanePicqDune
